Package: covr
Title: Test Coverage For Packages
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: "Jim Hester <james.f.hester@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Track test coverage for your package and (optionally)
    upload the results to a coverage service like codecov or coveralls.
    Compatible with any testing methodology or framework.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    methods
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    rex,
    devtools,
    httr,
    crayon,
    htmltools
Suggests:
    R6,
    knitr,
    shiny (>= 0.11.1),
    testthat,
    rstudioapi (>= 0.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
